prompts.frontCover: A charming, slightly wobbly cartoon-style layer cake, precariously balanced and leaning like the Tower of Pisa, its layers melting slightly into each other. On top of the cake, instead of candles, a single, very tired-looking cartoon snail with a party hat on its shell is slowly making its way across the frosting, leaving a shimmering trail. The text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, slightly whimsical handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color across the center of the cake. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, with soft, flowing pastel colors (pinks, soft yellows, light blues), visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the cake and snail, creating a lighthearted and handmade feel.
